Package: MinirhizotronR
Type: Package
Title: Extracting Depth Resolved Metrics from Minirhizotron Root Scans
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Authors@R: c(
    person("Johannes", "Cunow", , "johannes.cunow@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  )
Maintainer: Johannes Cunow <johannes.cunow@gmail.com>
Description: With MinirhizotronR, analyzing root scans from minirhizotron tubes becomes a piece of cake. It enables the user to extract various root metrics and relate them to a depth distribution, or assess rotational biases. It relies on outside handling of Image Segmentation. 
